quran[9{c,v,t}:
34,49,keh do ke haq aachuka aur ( mabood ) baatil nah to pehli baar peda karsaktha hai aur nah dobarah peda kere ga
34,50,keh do ke agar mein gumraah hon to meri gumraahi ka zarrar mujhi ko hai. aur agar hadaayat par hon to yeh is ka tufail hai jo mera perwar-digaar meri taraf wahi bhejta hai. be shak woh suneney wala ( aur ) nazdeek hai
34,51,aur kash tum dekho jab yeh ghabra jayen ge to ( azaab se ) bach nahi saken ge aur nazdeek hi se pakar liye jayen ge
34,52,aur kahin ge ke hum is par imaan le aeye aur ( ab ) itni daur se un ka haath imaan ke lainay ko kyonkr poanch sakta hai
34,53,aur pehlay to is se inkaar karte rahay aur ban dekhe daur hi se ( zan ke ) teer chillate rahay
34,54,aur un mein aur un ki khwahish ki cheezon mein parda haail kardiya gaya jaissa ke pehlay un ke hum jnson sekiya gaya woh bhi uljan mein daalnay walay shak mein parre hue they
35,1,sab tareef khuda hi ko ( sazawar hai ) jo asmano aur zameen ka peda karne wala ( aur ) firshton ko qasid bananay wala hai jin ke do do aur teen teen aur chaar chaar par hain. woh ( apni ) makhloqaat mein jo chahta hai berhata hai. be shak khuda har cheez par Qadir hai
35,2,khuda jo apni rehmat ( ka darwaaza ) khol day to koi is ko band karne wala nahi. aur jo band kardey to is ke baad koi is ko kholnay wala nahi. aur woh ghalib hikmat wala hai
35,3,logo khuda ke jo tum par ahsanat hain un ko yaad karo.kiya khuda ke siwa koi aur khaaliq ( aur Razaq hai ) jo tum ko aasman aur zameen se rizaq day. is ke siwa koi mabood nahi pas tum kahan behke phirtay ho ?
